{"tid":2428952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅志祥復出首天認購200箱菠蘿 內地網民批評：別再來撈金","createTime":"2021-03-02T02:53:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T09:49:11.000Z","uid":39464,"like":115,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"7526a7ff1e9eafa52df63632d28ca08b5bfae428","tid":2428952,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T02:53:24.000Z","msg":"羅志祥去年4月被舊愛周揚青以「毀滅式」宣布分手，大爆他私生活混亂，重創他的形象及事業。停工近10個月的羅志祥，上月27日在YouTube開設頻道發放影片，正式宣布復出；同日，他認購了200箱菠蘿挺果農。想不到事件牽扯到兩岸政治局勢，不少內地網民也在微博批評羅志祥，「知道中國復出無望轉抱台灣觀眾大腿」、「他願意買就買吧，反正別再來大陸撈金就好。」、「大陸復出無望，這是破罐子破摔了？」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20210301/1614600658605/%e7%be%85%e5%bf%97%e7%a5%a5%e5%be%a9%e5%87%ba%e9%a6%96%e5%a4%a9%e8%aa%8d%e8%b3%bc200%e7%ae%b1%e8%8f%a0%e8%98%bf-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e7%b6%b2%e6%b0%91%e6%89%b9%e8%a9%95-%e5%88%a5%e5%86%8d%e4%be%86%e6%92%88%e9%87%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20210301%2F1614600658605%2F%25e7%25be%2585%25e5%25bf%2597%25e7%25a5%25a5%25e5%25be%25a9%25e5%2587%25ba%25e9%25a6%2596%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e8%25aa%258d%25e8%25b3%25bc200%25e7%25ae%25b1%25e8%258f%25a0%25e8%2598%25bf-%25e5%2585%25a7%25e5%259c%25b0%25e7%25b6%25b2%25e6%25b0%2591%25e6%2589%25b9%25e8%25a9%2595-%25e5%2588%25a5%25e5%2586%258d%25e4%25be%2586%25e6%2592%2588%25e9%2587%2591&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt10kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=2e797570\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20210301%2F1614600658605%2F%25e7%25be%2585%25e5%25bf%2597%25e7%25a5%25a5%25e5%25be%25a9%25e5%2587%25ba%25e9%25a6%2596%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e8%25aa%258d%25e8%25b3%25bc200%25e7%25ae%25b1%25e8%258f%25a0%25e8%2598%25bf-%25e5%2585%25a7%25e5%259c%25b0%25e7%25b6%25b2%25e6%25b0%2591%25e6%2589%25b9%25e8%25a9%2595-%25e5%2588%25a5%25e5%2586%258d%25e4%25be%2586%25e6%2592%2588%25e9%2587%2591&h=1f04c06e\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20210301/1614600658605/%e7%be